  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04 trigger)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set to 3. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed; the factor 'Equivalency of input parameters' carries factorStatus 'not-assessed' because the assessment team judged that input parameter equivalency does not apply to this purely predictive COU — a rationale that warrants 'not-applicable' encoding rather than 'not-assessed'. The mismatch between the elevated MRL and the unassessed factor constitutes the W-EP-04 epistemic gap. Decision: Accepted.",
