    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package based on the twelve assessed factors, noting that the majority of verification factors achieved their required levels and that Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed. The unassessed 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor was informally treated as inapplicable by the team without formally encoding it as 'not-applicable', leaving an unresolved epistemic gap at MRL 3. The decision to accept despite this gap is the subject of W-EP-04 scrutiny.",
